This is the Privacy and Cookie Statement for TodayTix, Ltd ("TodayTix"), our website hosted at
www.todaytix.com/uk/privacy-policy
(**"we,"** **"us,"** and **"Our Site"**) and each of our web and mobile applications that we make available from time to time (**"Applications"** ). Our Site and Applications are operated by or on behalf of TodayTix.
This Statement, and any other documents referred to in it, set out:
