Privacy Policy for TodayTix
Last Updated: May 3, 2024
TodayTix, Inc. ("
we
" or "
us
" or "
TodayTix
" or the "
Company
")¬† is committed to protecting your privacy. We have prepared this Privacy Policy to describe our practices regarding the Personal Data (as defined below) we collect from users of our website, located at www.todaytix.com, our mobile applications and our widgets, and your other interactions with us (all of which are collectively referred to herein as our "
Services
").¬† Our
Terms of Use
